    "created_at": "2017-02-08T07:47:16Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-03-17T07:36:40Z",
    "body": "cc #39450, which is on the declarative macros 2.0 [roadmap](https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/39412#issuecomment-277867338).\r\n\r\n@kmcallister @michaelwoerister \r\nThe current plan here is to add more span information to \"interpolated tokens\" (`NoDelim` token trees in the macros 2.0 framework) and make the parser smart enough to know when to use e.g. the span of the meta-variable `$val` versus the span where `$val` came from.",
